  "title": "📈 Product Marketing Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>✨ Searching for Product Marketing Coordinator</strong></p><p><strong>Type: Full-Time</strong></p><p><strong>🌱 About the Opportunity</strong></p><p>We are an outsourced marketing company that represents multiple clients to help market their products</p><p><strong>🧠 What We Provide</strong></p><p>- 1-to-1 mentorship</p><p>- Fun and interactive environment</p><p>- Clear advancement criteria</p><p>- Multiple clients you can work for</p><p>- Overseas expansion and trips</p><p>- Team bonding activities to bond with your colleagues</p><p><strong>🔧 What You’ll Do</strong></p><p>- Learn about the clients products and market their products</p><p>- Have the opportunity to guide new individuals</p><p>- Build leadership skills and lead a team</p><p><strong>💡 You’re a Great Fit If You…</strong></p><p>- Have the willingness to learn</p><p>- Have the courage to try and the attitude to learn</p><p>- No prior experience required — we look for attitude and develop skillsets.</p><p>📌 <strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>- The ability to work collaboratively</p><p>- Adaptable and have the leadership to lead the team</p><p><strong>📨 How to Apply</strong></p><p><strong>Contact Justin Yiew at 98371106 on WhatsApp or telegram</strong></p>",
